    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《拖延之影》是一款以叙事剧情为主的游戏，玩家将围绕“以后再说”的主题寻找隐藏的物品。探索精心绘制的2D漫画世界，与神秘的猫形生物玩躲猫猫。游戏初期轻松、欢乐，但最终将演变为一场关于内心冲突与拖延的阴影的深刻旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229910/extras/e7994c86773c9a3b3423e01aacbf49bd.poster.avif?t=1768405215\" width=900 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229910/extras/e7994c86773c9a3b3423e01aacbf49bd.webm?t=1768405215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229910/extras/e7994c86773c9a3b3423e01aacbf49bd.mp4?t=1768405215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的寻找物品体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在满是杂物的公寓中寻找一只可爱的生物，途中或许还能发现隐藏的秘密。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事简短而意味深远 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏时长约为30分钟，为玩家带来前所未有的独特体验。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >沉浸式2D漫画风格</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有图像均以黑白手绘呈现，细腻中透着淡淡的忧郁。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超现实旅程</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 踏上一段简短却富有冲击力且充满惊喜的旅程。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >轻松易上手</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 只需使用鼠标左键即可游玩，毫无技术门槛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229910/extras/7e0f187626d380edb9834d7de62dda26.poster.avif?t=1768405215\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229910/extras/7e0f187626d380edb9834d7de62dda26.webm?t=1768405215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229910/extras/7e0f187626d380edb9834d7de62dda26.mp4?t=1768405215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
